(7, 'I KEKER TEKEN I LUTUNG', '<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ada kon&eacute; katuturan satua &ldquo;I K&eacute;k&eacute;r Tek&eacute;n I Lutung&rdquo;. Di alas&eacute; kaja, ada kon&eacute; I K&eacute;k&eacute;r sedekan indeng-indeng ngalih amah-amahan. Kacerita teka I Lutung maekin I K&eacute;k&eacute;r. &ldquo;Wih K&eacute;k&eacute;r, n&eacute; masan langit&eacute; terak, nguding Iba jeg mokoh lemuh? Wak&eacute; k&eacute;n&eacute; men berag t&eacute;gr&eacute;s, lepas kena wake amah-amahan&rdquo;. Masaut I K&eacute;k&eacute;r, &ldquo;Saja Lutung. Yen wake dini g&eacute;n klincakklincak, saja jaa sing ada amah-amahan. Wak&eacute; ditu selat danu wake biasa ngalih amah-amahan. Ditu ada alas beten paekan danu, sawai kena iusan y&eacute;h danu mapuara lemek. Yen Iba ditu ngalih amah, whowohan sedeng nasak-nasak&rdquo; Keto I K&eacute;k&eacute;r. &ldquo;Aduh K&eacute;k&eacute;r, ajak ja wake kema, pang misian gigis awak wak&eacute;n&eacute;. Jeg k&eacute;n&eacute; sing ada apa-apa dini&rdquo; K&eacute;to I Lutung ngidih olas tek&eacute;n I K&eacute;k&eacute;r. Masaut I K&eacute;k&eacute;r, &ldquo;Nah lamun saja k&eacute;to idep Cain&eacute;, lan ajaka men kema&rdquo;.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Masaut buin I Lutung, &ldquo;Men k&eacute;ngk&eacute;n caran&eacute; jani, mapan selat danu? Kudiang abet&eacute; pang sida neked ditu?&rdquo; I K&eacute;k&eacute;r nimbal, &ldquo;Elah ban wake ngenehang. Mai iba men&eacute;k, dini maenjekan di tegil wak&eacute;n&eacute;, laut iba magandong, jalan ajaka makeber ajak dadua&rdquo;. &ldquo;O&hellip; nah nah.&rdquo; Keto I Lutung tur men&eacute;k magandong di tundun&eacute; I K&eacute;k&eacute;r. Puuuu&hellip;rrrr, &eacute;nggal I K&eacute;k&eacute;r makeber lakar ngliwatin danu ngandong I Lutung. &ldquo;Ad&eacute;ng-ad&eacute;ng K&eacute;k&eacute;r, aduh&hellip; jejeh wake k&eacute;n Iba sriat-sriut&rdquo; Keto I Lutung ngraos, sag&eacute;t &eacute;nggal ia neked di alas ulun danun&eacute;. I Lutung macebur, laut makecos men&eacute;k punyan lisah ngalap buah lisah suba kuning. Buin ia makecos ka punyan nyam bun&eacute;, buin ka punyan nangkan&eacute; kanti uleg-ulegan ia bes netekan neda who-wohan.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Kacerita k&eacute;to gega&eacute;n&eacute; I Lutung di alas ulun danun&eacute;, lega pesan ia sadina-dina nepukin who-wohan an&eacute; ma&eacute;ndahan tur suba pada tasak. Saja jeg motah ia ngamah buah tusing cara diugas di tongosn&eacute; I mnaluan. Kacerita I K&eacute;k&eacute;r sedekan masandekan suud ng&eacute;k&eacute;h tetani an&eacute; biasa tedana tur makrana ia mokoh siteng. Teka masi I Liutung maekin I K&eacute;k&eacute;r tur ngraos, &ldquo;Suksma K&eacute;k&eacute;r, Iba suba ngajak wak&eacute; mai di tongos an&eacute; liu pesan misi who-wohan&rdquo;. Masaut I K&eacute;k&eacute;r. &ldquo;Nah Lutung, Kai lega masi maan mapitulung tek&eacute;n Iba. Mara aminggu Iba dini suba nyalingah, muan Iban&eacute; bag, basing Iban&eacute; suba enting, maciri Iba suba ngamokohan. I Lutung matakon, &ldquo;K&eacute;ngk&eacute;n idep Iban&eacute; K&eacute;k&eacute;r? Jalan jenek lantas dini nyak! Kai demen pesan dini, eda suba buin malipetan ka tongos&eacute; pidan, apang Kai mokohan malu bin abedik!&rdquo; I K&eacute;k&eacute;r nyautin, &ldquo;Lutung, wake ada perlu abedik, buin mani lakar mulih, yen Iba kan dini, pang wake dogen mulih bin mani nah! Iba selegang suba malu dini!&rdquo; Mara k&eacute;to I K&eacute;k&eacute;r ngraos, sada jejeh kenehn&eacute; I Lutung lakar kalahina ban I K&eacute;k&eacute;r mulih. Ngomong buin I Lutung, &ldquo;Eda ja malu mulih K&eacute;k&eacute;r, Kai sing lung asan&eacute; dini padidian. Bin aminggu kai lakar milu masi mulih.&rdquo; Mara k&eacute;to I Lutung mapangidih, maanggutan I K&eacute;k&eacute;r, nyak lakar buin aminggun&eacute; mabalik ka umahn&eacute; I malu.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Kacerita jani, I K&eacute;k&eacute;r sedek masiksikan, &ldquo;Ih Iba Lutung, mungpung ngoyong, Iba boisa ngalihin kutun wak&eacute;n&eacute;? Ndas wak&eacute;n&eacute; genit marukrukan. Tulungin jep alihin kutu!&rdquo; &ldquo;O&hellip; nah, Kai mula demen ngalih kutu. Mai alihina ja!&rdquo; K&eacute;to kon&eacute; I Lutung masaut laut maekin I K&eacute;k&eacute;r tur ngalihin kutu. Saja liu bakatanga kutun I K&eacute;k&eacute;r&eacute; kanti I K&eacute;k&eacute;r pules leplep sirsir angina. I Lutung ngrenggeng ia makeneh, &ldquo;B&eacute;h &hellip; sedeng demena id&eacute;w&eacute;k nongos dini, liu gati maan dedemekan, suba lakar ajaka mulih ban I K&eacute;k&eacute;r. Paling melah jani butbut bulunn&eacute; pang ya sing nyidang makeber.&rdquo; Keto kenehn&eacute; I Lutung laut sahasa ia mutbutin bulun kampid I K&eacute;k&eacute;r&eacute; kanti ulagan kampidn&eacute; tan pabulum. Jani tengkejut I K&eacute;k&eacute;r tur ngraos, Aduh &hellip; Cai Lutung, miratdana Cai tek&eacute;n Wak&eacute;. Nak k&eacute;ngk&eacute;n budin Iban&eacute; dadi sahasa mutbut bulun kampid wak&eacute;n&eacute;? Sing pean Iba marasa suba katulungin kanti mokoh buka jani?&rdquo;</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Mara k&eacute;to I K&eacute;k&eacute;r ngraos, masaut jani I Lutung k&eacute;n&eacute;. &ldquo;Wih.. K&eacute;k&eacute;r, bes mara wake segeran maan tetedan liu dini, suba Iba nagih mulih. Wak&eacute; nu meled nongos dini. Yen suba telah bulun kampid Iban&eacute; s&eacute; tusing Iba nyidang makeber. Lan ajaka ngoyong malu dini!&rdquo;. Nimbal I K&eacute;k&eacute;r kasakitan. &ldquo;Iba mula tusing ngelah pangrasa, tusing bisa ngwales tresnan anak. Nah&hellip; wak&eacute; sing ja k&eacute;ngk&eacute;n. Kema suba kalahin ngalih amah-amahan!&rdquo; K&eacute;to tamp&eacute;sanga piolasan I K&eacute;k&eacute;r&eacute; ban I Lutung. Sabilang semeng muah sanja, masiksikan I K&eacute;k&eacute;r sambilanga namuhin kampidn&eacute; kanti suba buin tumbuh bulu.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Gelising satua, jani aliha I Lutung ban I K&eacute;k&eacute;r, sasuban&eacute; matemu ngomong I K&eacute;k&eacute;r, &ldquo;Wih&hellip; Lutung, Wak&eacute; jani lakar mulih, men Iba k&eacute;ngk&eacute;n? Lakar milu mulih apa tusing? Lamun milu mai men&eacute;k di tegil wak&eacute;n&eacute;!&rdquo; Mara k&eacute;to masaut I Lutung, &ldquo;Nah kai lakar milu mulih&rdquo;. Men&eacute;k jani ia magandong laut kakeberang ban I k&eacute;k&eacute;r. Sriat-sriut gencang pesan kebern&eacute; I K&eacute;k&eacute;r kanti I Lutung ngutah-utah. Jani suba teked di tengahing danu, dadi masriut I K&eacute;k&eacute;r tuun, maencegan di batun&eacute; l&eacute;mp&eacute;h. Mara mar&eacute;r&eacute;n matakon kon&eacute; I Lutung, &ldquo;Wih&hellip; K&eacute;k&eacute;r to nguda Iba tuun dini?&rdquo; Kasautin ban I K&eacute;k&eacute;r, &ldquo;Mareren malu jep Lutung. Awak wak&eacute;n&eacute; ungkeb pesan, wake lakar manjus malu dik Iba dini malu negak!&rdquo; Kato I K&eacute;k&eacute;r tur masliuk di y&eacute;h danun&eacute; maplukpukan ia manjus tur mambuh.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Kacerita n&eacute; jani, sawir&eacute;h I Lutung basangn&eacute; betek tur sirsir angina di duur batun&eacute;, kiap ia ayag-oyog nguyuk laut pules leplep. Jani I K&eacute;k&eacute;r pesu kenehn&eacute; ngwalesin kacorahan I Lutung&eacute; dugas kampidn&eacute; kabutbut. Kalahina I Lutung makeber ban I K&eacute;k&eacute;r. I K&eacute;k&eacute;r suba nambung sambilanga nged&eacute;kin I Lutung. &ldquo;Wih&hellip; Lutung, jani suba Iba ngemasin buah karman Iban&eacute;. Wak&eacute; lakar mulih padidi. Dini suba Iba muponin buahn&eacute;!&rdquo; Makrapangan jani I Lutung bangun tur gelur-gelur ngaukin I K&eacute;k&eacute;r. &ldquo;Aduh&hellip; K&eacute;k&eacute;r&hellip; K&eacute;k&eacute;r&hellip;. Ngidih olas alih kai mai K&eacute;k&eacute;r! Kai ngidih pelih pang sanget, ajak kai mulih K&eacute;k&eacute;r! Kai tusing bani dini padidian! Tulung&hellip;. Tulung&hellip;. Tulungin kai K&eacute;k&eacute;r!&rdquo; Keto I Lutung ngidih olas, nanging tusing runguanga ban I K&eacute;k&eacute;r. I K&eacute;k&eacute;r nerusang makeber ngalahin I Lutung di tengah danun&eacute;. K&eacute;to pamuputn&eacute;, I Lutung an&eacute; miratdana muponin kacirahan&eacute;.</span></p>', 'keker.png', NULL),
(8, 'I BOJOG TEKEN I KEDIS SANGSIAH', '<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ada kon&eacute; truturan satua, I Bojog tek&eacute;n I Kedis Sangsiah&rdquo;. Kacerita, ada kon&eacute; kedis sangsiah luh muani, itep ia ngajang sebun, sawir&eacute;h suba lakar ng&eacute;r&eacute;ang mataluh. Mula tuah sawatek kedis&eacute; dueg ia nga&eacute; sebun, an&eacute; malakar ban don-donan, luir&eacute; don ambengan, padang an&eacute; dawa-dawa, somi, muah an&eacute; l&eacute;nan. Disuban&eacute; pragat, asri pesan pangenahn&eacute;, waluya buka bubun&eacute; magantung di carawg kayun&eacute; tegeh ngenjik, misi bolongan an&eacute; dadi jalan i kedis pesu-mulih. Punyan kayu sig tongos i kedis&eacute; masebun, sedeng nedenga mabuah, an&eacute; dadi amah-amahan bojog. Ento makrana liu bojog&eacute; teka ka tongos&eacute; ento ngalih amah. Katuju i kedis matolihan, ada kon&eacute; bojog teka maekin, laut i kedis matakon, &ldquo;Oo Cai Bojog, luung pesan kinyukan bungut Cain&eacute; ngamah buah kayu an&eacute; suba tasak-tasak. Ambul apa ja likad tongosn&eacute;, prasida baan Cai ngalih. Sak&eacute;wala ada an&eacute; kimudang wak&eacute; di ati, sawir&eacute;h gega&eacute;n Cain&eacute; tuah ngalih amah dog&eacute;nan, diastu Cai tusing ngelah umah. Ngapung pesan idup Cain&eacute;, witeh setata ngandelang paga&eacute;n anak l&eacute;nan. Luir&eacute; amah-amahan, umah, ento makejang an&eacute; puponin Cai, diastun tusing katuyuhan d&eacute;w&eacute;k Cain&eacute; padidi.&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Mal&eacute;nan pesan tek&eacute;n unduk wak&eacute;n&eacute;, en&eacute; umah an&eacute; tongosin wak&eacute;, mula ulihan katuyuhan padidi. Wak&eacute; ngajak somah, suba dadi kekasuban i manusa. Yan suba i manusa nepukin umah awak&eacute;, an&eacute; kaloktah madan &ldquo;Sebun Kedis Sangsiah, tusing gigisan gegaok paidepan&eacute;. Yan kapining Cai, makejang i manusa marasa geting, sawir&eacute;h Cai kaucap meranan saluir tanem tuuh&eacute;&rdquo;. K&eacute;to pangumanuman I Kedis Sangsiah&eacute; marep kapining I Bojog. Mara k&eacute;to I Kedis, karasa sanget nganistang ia I Bojog, laut ia masaut sada banggras, &ldquo;Ih, Iba kedis nista, mula k&eacute;to bikas Iban&eacute;, tuara marasa tek&eacute;ning d&eacute;w&eacute;k nista, tuah bisa ngon&eacute;k jel&eacute;k anak l&eacute;nan, sak&eacute;wala tusing marasa tek&eacute;n jel&eacute;k&eacute; di d&eacute;w&eacute;k Iban&eacute;. Marasa k&eacute; Iba, yaning Iba sedekan ngalih amah-amahan, ngalih buah padi, an&eacute; dadi mertanin manusa, kanti lisik baan Iba muut, wastu i manusa k&eacute;langan merta utama, pamragat gumin&eacute; terak sarang.&rdquo;</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">N&eacute; Iba sanget ngajumang d&eacute;w&eacute;k, ulihan marasa ririh nga&eacute; sebun, kanti ngardi gegoak i manusa, kadaut idepa&eacute;. K&eacute;wala Iba tusing marasa ngrusak don-donan abian i manusan&eacute;. Ada sl&eacute;pan, padang gajah, don padi enu di adegan. Ento makejang usakang Iba. Cutetn&eacute;, Iba tusing ja gigis ngardi usak di gumin&eacute;. N&eacute; Iba apang nawang, diastu kai orahang Iba tusing bisa nga&eacute; umah, k&eacute;wala leluhur kain&eacute;, ta&eacute;n mamanjakin Ida Betara Rama, dugas Ida ngebug Sang Prabu Rahwana di Lengkapura, mawastu kalah Ida Sang Prabu. Buina leluhur kain&eacute;, prasida ngurug pasih, nga&eacute; kreteg an&eacute; madan Situbanda, mawastu elah leluhur kain&eacute; ngiring Ida Betara Rama magegebug ka Lengkapura.&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">K&eacute;to nyen kaluihan leluhur kain&eacute;, mamanjak ring sang maraga utama, panrestian Hyang Wisnu. K&eacute;to pasaut I Bojog&eacute;, laut m&eacute;sb&eacute;s sebun I Kedis Sangsiah&eacute;, ked taluhn&eacute; nyag kacakcak. Suud k&eacute;to i bojog laut magedi ngungsi ka punyan kayun&eacute; l&eacute;nan. Ditu lantasan I Kedis Sangsiah sedih kingking, tan mari nyelsel d&eacute;w&eacute;k, nyambatang d&eacute;w&eacute;k tuna bagia.</span></p>', 'sangsiah.png', NULL),
(9, 'I CICING GUDIG', '<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ada kon&eacute; tuturan satua &ldquo;I Cicing Gudig&rdquo;. I Cicing Gudig, buka adann&eacute; berag t&eacute;gr&eacute;g tur keskes gudig, sing jalana mlispis ada dog&eacute;n anak ng&eacute;s&eacute;kang wiadin ngaltig. Sai-sai kon&eacute; ia maselselan, nyelselang buat kalacurann&eacute; tumbuh dadi cicing makejang anak&eacute; tuara ngiyengin. Sedek dina anu I Cicing Gudig mlispis di peken&eacute;. Ada kon&eacute; anak madaar di dagang nasin&eacute;, &eacute;nto kon&eacute; nengnenga men&eacute;k tuunanga dog&eacute;n. K&eacute;n&eacute; kenehn&eacute; I Cicing Gudig, \"Yan i d&eacute;w&eacute;k dadi manusa buka anak&eacute; &eacute;nto, k&eacute;nk&eacute;n ya legan nyet&eacute; ngamah, mab&eacute; soroh an&eacute; melah-melah. Ah ken&eacute; baan, nyanan peteng&eacute; lakar mabakti ka Pura Dalem, mapinunas tek&eacute;n Batari Durga apang dadi manusa.\"&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Kacrita suba peteng, mabakti kon&eacute; lantas I Cicing Gudig di Pura Dalem. Medal lantas Ida Betari Durga tur ngandika tek&eacute;n I Cicing Gudig, \"Ih iba Cicing Gudig, dadi iba ngacep nira, apa katunasang?\" Masaut I Cicing Gudig, \"Inggih paduka Betari, yan paduka Betari ledang, titiang mapinunas mangda dados manusa.\" Kalugra kon&eacute; pinunasn&eacute; I Cicing Gudig, lantas ia dadi jlema. D&eacute;ning I Cicing Gudig tusing bisa ngalih ga&eacute;, tusing pati kone ngamah. Mara-maraan ngamah ulihan maan mamaling. Pepes kon&eacute; ia katara mamaling. Lantas buin kon&eacute; ia mabakti di Pura Dalem. Medal lantas Ida Betari Durga tur ngandika tek&eacute;n I Cicing Gudig, \"Ih iba cai I Cicing Gudig, ng&eacute;nk&eacute;n dadi iba buin mai?\" Matur I Cicing Gudig, \"Inggih paduka Betari, titiang tan w&eacute;nten demen dados manusa panjak. Yan paduka Betari l&eacute;dang, titiang mapinunas mangda dados \"Patih\". Ida Betari Durga lugra. Nujuang pesan kon&eacute; dugas&eacute; &eacute;nto Ida Sang Prabu ngrereh buin adiri. I Cicing Gudig lantas kandikaang dadi Patih, tur I Cicing Gudig ngiring. \"B&eacute;h kew&eacute;h pesan i d&eacute;w&eacute;k dadi Pepatih, tusing ja maan ng&eacute;nk&eacute;n-ng&eacute;nk&eacute;n, begbeg pesan kandikayang tangkil ka puri. Yan i d&eacute;w&eacute;k dadi Anak Agung, k&eacute;nk&eacute;n ya legan nyet&eacute; nund&eacute;n-nund&eacute;n dog&eacute;n.\" K&eacute;to kenehn&eacute; I Cicing Gudig.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Gelisan satua &eacute;nggal, nyanan petengn&eacute; buin kon&eacute; ia mabakti di Pura Dalem, mapinunasang apang dadi Anak Agung. Ida Betari Durga lugra, lantas patuh pesan kon&eacute; goban I Cicing Gudig&eacute; tek&eacute;n warna Ida Sang Prabu. Kacrita Sang Prabu lunga kon&eacute; ida jagi maboros ka alas&eacute;, macelig kon&eacute; I Cicing Gudig ka puri. D&eacute;ning patuh goban I Cicing Gudig&eacute; tek&eacute;n Ida Sang Prabu, dadi kasengguh Ida Sang Prabu kon&eacute; ia baan I Patih muah tek&eacute;n prayogian&eacute; an&eacute; l&eacute;n-l&eacute;nan. Matur I Patih saha bakti, \"Titiang mamitang lugra Ratu Sang Prabu, punapi awinan dados Cokor I Ratu paragayan tulak saking paburuan?\" Masaut I Cicing Gudig, \"K&eacute;n&eacute; Patih, mawinan nira tulak, saking nira ngiringang sabdan Betara, tan kalugra nira malaksana mamati-mati. Kandikayang lantas nira tulak. To juru boros&eacute; ada pinunasa tek&eacute;n nira, tusing ngiring mantuk, krana kadunga suba makenaan. Nira nglugrahin, mawanan tan pairingan nira mulih.\" K&eacute;to pamunyinn&eacute; I Cicing Gudig, teka jag ngugu kon&eacute; I Patih muah panjak&eacute; an&eacute; l&eacute;n-l&eacute;nan.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Kacritayang jani sai-sai kon&eacute; I Cicing Gudig ngraosin anak mawikara. R&eacute;h Cicing gudig tuara nawang lud, makejang wikaran anak&eacute; pelih baana ngundukang, an&eacute; patut menang kalahanga, anak patut kalah menanganga. To makrana kaupet kon&eacute; I Cicing Gudig dadi Agung, sawaiwai ngencanin anak mawikara dog&eacute;n. Yan I D&eacute;w&eacute;k okan Anak Agung, k&eacute;nk&eacute;n ya demen&eacute;, kema mai malali iringang parekan, di k&eacute;nk&eacute;nne magandong, buina tusing pesan ngitungan apan-apan, sajawaning ngamah tek&eacute;n malali dog&eacute;n. Nyanan petengn&eacute;, mabakti kon&eacute; buin I Cicing Gudig di Pura Dalem, mapinunas apang dadi okan Anak Agung. Ida Betari Durga lugra. Patuh gobann&eacute; I Cicing Gudig buka warnanida Raden Mantri. Buin mani semengann&eacute;, maorta ilang kon&eacute; lantas Ida Raden Mantri. Ya sedeng ewana jeron&eacute; ngibukang Raden Mantri, delengdeleng kon&eacute; lantas I Cicing Gudig ngapuriang. R&eacute;h Cicing Gudig kasengguh Raden Mantri, makesiar keneh wang jeron&eacute; makejang.&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Kacrita jani I Cicing Gudig kapurukang malajah masastra. Dening asing ajahina muah takonina I Cicing Gudig tuara karoan baana apa, saapan kon&eacute; lantas gurun&eacute; ngemplangin I Cicing Gudig. \"Koang,\" k&eacute;to kon&eacute; aduhann&eacute; I Cicing Gudig. D&eacute;ning k&eacute;to, buin kon&eacute; pasangetina ngemplangin I Cicing Gudig. \"Koang,\" k&eacute;to kon&eacute; buin aduhann&eacute;. Buin kemplangina tur pasangetina, buin kon&eacute; I Cicing Gudig makoangan. Brangti kon&eacute; lantas gurunn&eacute;, lantas ia nyemak penyalin anggona nigtig I Cicing Gudig, kanti &eacute;nc&eacute;h-&eacute;nceh, mara kon&eacute; suudanga. Kacrita nyanan petengn&eacute; kon&eacute; ka Pura Dalem lantas I Cicing Gudig mabakti, mapinunas apang buin dadi Cicing Gudig buka jati mula. I Cicing Gudig lantas buin dadi cicing gudig.</span></p>', 'gudig.png', NULL),
(10, 'I CICING DADI RADEN GALUH', '<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ada katuturan satua &ldquo;I Cicing Dadi Rad&eacute;n Galuh&rdquo;. Kacerita ada Cicing kutu barakan, kema mai makejang ngulah. Di k&eacute;ngk&eacute;n&eacute; rebuta ia tek&eacute;n timpaln&eacute; an&eacute; segeran, kanti telah ia matatu, berekborok maidehan. Marasa ia k&eacute;weh likad, sawireh makejang pada geting nepukin. Makelo-kelo ngancan nyangetang penyakitn&eacute;, bulunn&eacute; telah aas, rigrig, tur awakn&eacute; terus meragan dog&eacute;n. Kacerita jani, nunas ica I Cicing ring Ida Sang Hyang Wasa, mapinunas apang suud nemuang papa neraka mapuara tusing setata kanistayang. Atur I Cicing, &ldquo;Inggih Ratu Sang Hyang Widi, titiang puniki damuh Paduka Betara marupa sato dahat nista, banget titiang nglungsur pasu&eacute;can I Ratu, l&eacute;dang mapaica pangruwatan ring d&eacute;w&eacute;k titiang, mangda n&eacute;nten kantun setata kanistayang&rdquo;. Kocapan, tedun Ida Betara Siwa, saha mawecana: &ldquo;Ih Iba Cicing, manira suba mireng atur Iban&eacute;. Men jani, k&eacute;ngk&eacute;n lakar pinunas Iban&eacute;, apa an&eacute; lakar tunas kapining manira?&rdquo;</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Matur I Cicing, &ldquo;Inggih Ratu Paduka Betara, titiang nunas ica, mangda titiang molihang merta, tur n&eacute;nten kaulah kakaonang, y&eacute;ning I Ratu l&eacute;dang, titiang nunas dados padma capah, mangda w&eacute;nten jadma mabanten irika, ngw&eacute;hin titiang tetedan&rdquo;. Ngandika Ida Betera Siwa, &ldquo;Nah Iba Cicing, manira nglugranin pinunas Iban&eacute;. Lautang Iba ngalih tongos di ulun pangkung gr&eacute;mb&eacute;ngan&eacute;, an&eacute; nepi ka margan&eacute;. Ditu Iba ngemit linggih Ida Betari Ganggad&eacute;wi, rabin maniran&eacute;. Sinah liu anak&eacute; maturan di tongos&eacute; ento! Makelo-kelo suba I Cicing masalin rupa dadi Padma Capah, tur nongos di ulun pangkung gr&eacute;mb&eacute;ngan&eacute;, an&eacute; paek ka jalan&eacute;. Liu tuah anak&eacute; mabanten, masaiban, ngaturang rarapan, mawastu I Cicing nepukin merta. Yen akudang bulan makelon&eacute; I Cicing suba dadi Padma Capah, dadi pesu papinehn&eacute; momo, sawireh kapineh yen ngandelang rarapan uli anak&eacute; an&eacute; ngliwat, kapah ya nepukin merta.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Kacerita ne jani, buin nunas ica ring Ida Sang Hyang Widi. &ldquo;Inggih Ratu Betara, san&eacute; mangkin titiang malih nunas ica ring Paduka Betara, mangda l&eacute;dang nyw&eacute;canin d&eacute;w&eacute;k titiang. Titiang nunas ica mangda titiang dados Rad&eacute;n Galuh, ring panegara Kertabumi. Ida Sang Prabu kaicalan putra san&eacute; dahat ka&eacute;man san&eacute; mangkin sampun s&eacute;da. Bilih titiang prasida ngawinang rered sungsut kayunidan&eacute;, ri sampun&eacute; titiang marupa Rad&eacute;n Galuh, san&eacute; kasengguh rauh saking suargan&rdquo;. Pinunas I Cicing ento kalugra masi olih Ida Betara Siwa, saja ia manadi Rad&eacute;n Galuh. Sang Prabu di Kertabumi, sedek kaduhkitan, wir&eacute;h katinggal s&eacute;da olih putran&eacute; an&eacute; tuah adiri tur istri. Ento makada Ida Sang Prabu tan mari kasungkawan, tambis-tambis ida kantu. Ri sedek Ida Sang Prabu Kertabumi ketangkilin baan para patih muah baudandanida, jag ada anak istri ayu tauh ngaturang raga, ngangken widyadari uling suargan.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Pengrauh anak&eacute; istri ane tuah panadian I Cicing, prasida murnayang pikayunan Ida Sang Prabu wir&eacute;h anak&eacute; istri ento misadia dadi panyilur Rad&eacute;n Galuh an&eacute; suba s&eacute;da. Ida Sang Prabu prajani l&eacute;dang pikayunan&eacute;, wir&eacute;h suba ada anak isteri dadi panyilur putran&eacute; an&eacute; suba nd&eacute;wata. Uli dinan&eacute; ento I Cicing an&eacute; marupa widyadari, madeg Rajaputri, mapes&eacute;ngan Rad&eacute;n Galuh. Ida Sang Prabu kaliwat sayang marep putran&eacute; ento. Rad&eacute;n Galuh panadian I Cicing&eacute;, buin nyangetang dog&eacute;n kamomoan&eacute;. Sedek dina melah, katuju tengah lemeng, buin I Cicing ngastawa Ida Sang Hyang Widi, nunas ica apang sida dadi d&eacute;wata, apang setata kamoling saluir an&eacute; edotanga wiadin kaacepang. Tedun kon&eacute; Ida Sang Hyang Siwa tur mawecana, &ldquo;Wih Iba Cicing, tui tuah Iba panumitisan sato, tusing ngelah rasa suksman idep, marep kapin paican Ida Sang Hyang Widi, setata ngulurin keneh momo droaka. Nah an&eacute; jani mabalik buin Iba dadi Cicing, tan paguna tan paaji, setata ngardi geting idep sang ngatonang. K&eacute;to wecanan Ida Betara Siwa, wastu Rad&eacute;n Galuh buin mabalik dadi cicing buka jati mula. K&eacute;to pikolih anak&eacute; an&eacute; setata ngulurin keneh momo, tusing ngelah rasa suksman idep.</span></p>', 'galuh.png', NULL),
(11, 'I BAWANG TEKÉN I KESUNA', '<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ada katuturan satua &ldquo;I Bawang teke&eacute;n I Kesuna&rdquo;. Kacerita ada anak makurenan, ngelah pianak dadua luh-luh. Pianakn&eacute; an&eacute; kelihan madan I Bawang, an&eacute; cerikan madan I Kesuna. Akuren ngoyong kon&eacute; di desa. Sewai-wai geginan&eacute; tuah maburuh ka uma. I Bawang tek&eacute;n I Kesuna matungkasan pesan kon&eacute; bikasn&eacute;. I Bawang anak jemet mega&eacute; tur demen nulungin reramann&eacute;. Dueg masi ia ngraos, sing ta&eacute;n ia ngraos an&eacute; jel&eacute;k-jel&eacute;k. Jemet melajahang raga, malajahin saluiring geginan dadi tugasn&eacute; dadi anak luh. Marengin m&eacute;m&eacute; megarapan di paon, metanding canang, muah an&eacute; l&eacute;nan. Melanan pesan ngajak adinn&eacute; I Kesuna. I Kesuna anak bobab, males maga&eacute;, demen pesan mapisuna.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Kacrita M&eacute;m&eacute;n&eacute; lakar luas ka peken, tund&eacute;na pianakn&eacute; nuunin padi laut nyemuh tur nebuk kanti apragatan. Disuban&eacute; I Bawang nuunang padi, tund&eacute;na I Kesuna nyemuh padi, k&eacute;n&eacute; raosn&eacute;. &ldquo;Jemuh nak&eacute; jani padin&eacute; I Kesuna!&rdquo; Masaut I Kesuna, &ldquo;Jemuh ja malu nyanan Icang ja nebuk&rdquo;. Suba tuh padin&eacute;, agia jani lakar nebuk padi. Ngraos I Bawang tek&eacute;n adinn&eacute;, &ldquo;Ih Kesuna, n&eacute; suba tuh jani padin&eacute;, dong &eacute;nggalang jani tebuk!&rdquo; Masaaut buin I Kesuna, &ldquo;Nh tebuk ja malu, nyanan Icang ja nglesung&rdquo;. Suba suud nebuk, buin I Kesuna tund&eacute;na, &ldquo;Jani lesung anak&eacute; jijih&eacute; Kesuna!&rdquo;. Masaut I Ksuna &ldquo;Nah, lesung ja malu nyanan Icang ja ngindangang!&rdquo;</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Kacerita, kanti kenyel suba I Bawang nund&eacute;n adinn&eacute;, nanging tusing pesan ada kalaksanayang. Sedek dina anu, I Bawang mara suud nglesung padi laut kayeh sambilanga ngaba jun anggona ngalih y&eacute;h. I Kesuna, mapan tau tek&eacute;n m&eacute;m&eacute;n&eacute; lakar teka uli peken, uapa awakn&eacute; ban wot, apang nyak cara anak suud nebuk padi. Teka jani m&eacute;m&eacute;n&eacute; uli peken. Tengkejt nepukin I Kesuna jengis ngoahang I Bawang tusing pesan nyak magarapan. &ldquo;Ih M&eacute;, pocol M&eacute;m&eacute; nglah pianak buka I Bawang. Sing pesan nyak marengin tiang magarapan. Tonden suud nebuk, suba kalaina Icang kayeh. Eda pesan ia baanga gapgapan, yen teka uli kayeh, jeg siam nasn&eacute; ban y&eacute;h anget. Saja gedeg m&eacute;m&eacute;n&eacute; tur nga&eacute; y&eacute;h anget. Mara teka I Bawang kayeh, jeg siama ban y&eacute;h anget maduluran munyi an&eacute; kasar-kasar, nundung I Bawang apanga magedi uli jumahn&eacute;. I Bawang laut megedi sambilanga ngeling sigsigan. Di suban&eacute; ngutang umah, murang-murang lampah ia tusing karwan pajalan&eacute;, kanti teked di sisin tukad&eacute; makeneh ia nganyudang awak.&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ditu kon&eacute; teka I Kedis Crukcuk Kuning maekin I Bawang. Ngraos I Bawang, &ldquo;Wih, Iba Kedis Crukcuk. Apa kon&eacute; pangenan Wak&eacute; urip di gumin&eacute;? Wake sing enu ngelah nyama beraya. Yen tuah Iba lega, amah suba wak&eacute;, apang &eacute;nggal mati!&rdquo; K&eacute;to I Bawang buin nglanturang sambilanga magending, &ldquo;Crukcuk-crukcuk Kuning Cilalongan, dong gotol ja tendas ka&eacute;n&eacute;!&rdquo; &ldquo;Tol&hellip;.&rdquo; Saja gotola sirah I Bawang&eacute; ban I Crukcuk, sag&eacute;t bek kon&eacute; misi soroh bunga emas Apa kad&eacute;n demen atin&eacute; I Bawang. Buin ia magending, &ldquo;Crukcuk-crukcuk Kuning Cilalongan, dong gotol ja kuping ka&eacute;n&eacute;!&rdquo; &ldquo;Tol&hellip;.&rdquo; Saja gotola kuping I Bawang&eacute;, sag&eacute;t maka duang an&eacute;h kon&eacute; misi subeng emas. Buin I Bawang magending, &ldquo;Crukcuk-crukcuk Kuning Cilalongan, dong gotol ja baong ka&eacute;n&eacute;!&rdquo; &ldquo;Tol&hellip;.&rdquo; Saja gotola baong I Bawang&eacute; ban I Crukcuk, sag&eacute;t misi kon&ldquo;Crukcuk-crukcuk Kuning Cilalongan, dong gotol ja tendas ka&eacute;n&eacute;!&rdquo; &ldquo;Tol&hellip;.&rdquo; Saja gotola sirah I Bawang&eacute; ban I Crukcuk, sag&eacute;t bek kon&eacute; misi soroh bunga emas. Kalung emas. K&eacute;to salanturnyan&eacute;, liman&eacute; misi galang emas, jrijin&eacute; pada tetelu kiwa tengan misi bungkung emas. Maimbuh kamen sutra, sandal tinjik, muah baju kain brokat melah gati. Suba liu ia maan pepayasan uli I Crukcuk Kuning, kisik-kisik I Bawang ngojog ka umah dadongn&eacute;. Tusing ia ta&eacute;n mulih ka umah reramann&eacute;.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Kacerita jani I Kesuna nuju ka peken mabelanja, matemu ia ngajak embokn&eacute; an&eacute; mapanganggo melah-melah, laut ia nakonang uli dija maan panganggo buka k&eacute;to. Disuban&eacute; orahina tek&eacute;n I Bawang, ditu laut I Kesuna metu kaloban kenehn&eacute;. Edot pesan ia ngelah penganggo muah papayas an an&eacute; bungah buka an&eacute; gelahanga ban I Bawang. Sawir&eacute;h buka k&eacute;to, ditu I Kesuna ngorahin memenn&eacute; nigtig ukudan&eacute; apang kanti babak belur. &ldquo;Ih meme, icing dot pesan ngelah pepayasan cara I Bawang. Jani &eacute;nggalang siam tiang ban y&eacute;h anget, tigtig tur tundung icing cara I Bawang, icing lakar ngutang awak apang katemu ajak I Kedis Crukcuk, lakar ngidih emas-emasan!</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Sawir&eacute;h patuh momo kenehn&eacute; ngajak m&eacute;m&eacute;nn&eacute;, saja ia kasiam ban y&eacute;h anget laut katigtig tur tundunga apang &eacute;nggal magedi uli jumahn&eacute;. Sesuban&eacute; katigtig, lantas ia ngeling sengu-sengu nuju ka tukad&eacute; apang katemu ngajak I Kedis Crukcuk Kuning. Sasuban&eacute; katemu, ngomong I Kesuna, &ldquo;Wih Iba Crukcuk Kuning, wak&eacute; dot pesan ngelah pepayasan cara I Bawang, &eacute;nggalang cotot wak&eacute;!&rdquo; Mara k&eacute;to pangidih I Kesunan&eacute;, agia I Crukcuk Kuning ngotol ukudan I Kesunan&eacute;, nanging sing ja isinina emas-emasan. Tengkejut tur jerit-jerit I Kesuna, sawir&eacute;h sasuban&eacute; ia kacotot ban I Crukcuk Kuning, magenepan isin awakn&eacute;, soroh gumatatgumitit an&eacute; nyejehin. Ada lelipi, ada lelintah, ada teledu, ada tabuan, kalejengking, muah an&eacute; l&eacute;nan. Melaib ia jerit-jerit mulihn&eacute;. Mara lakar macelep ka umahn&eacute;, suba I Kesuna kacotot ban I lelipi gadang, kanti ngemasin mati.</span></p>', 'bawang.png', NULL),
(12, 'KAMBING TAKUTIN MACAN', '<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Kacerita ada kambing madan Ni M&eacute;saba. Ngelah kon&eacute; ia panak aukud madan Ni Wingsali. Luas kon&eacute; ia ka alas&eacute;, ngalih amahamahan an&eacute; nguda-nguda. Panakn&eacute;, Ni Wingsali bareng masi ka alas&eacute;. Tan kacerita di jalan, teked ajaka dadua di alas&eacute;. Bih, demen pesan Ni M&eacute;saba ajak Ni Wingsali, nepukin tetedan ma&eacute;ndahan tur makejang sarwa nguda. Sedeng iteha ia ngamah, makasiab Ni Wingsali nepukin buron tawah. Malaib Ni Wingsali di durin m&eacute;m&eacute;n&eacute;, sambilanga matakon. &rdquo;Ih.., M&eacute;m&eacute;&hellip;.m&eacute;m&eacute;&hellip;.ada buron tawah, to to ya M&eacute;, ikutn&eacute; lantang, goban&eacute; a&eacute;ng, nyeh tiyang m&eacute;m&eacute;..&rdquo; Masaut lantas Ni M&eacute;saba, &rdquo;Ento tuah madan I Macan. Nah k&eacute;n&eacute; jani Cning, entegang sebeng&eacute; apang cara anak sakti, ento jalan anggon nayanin I Macan, an&eacute; setata malaksana corah&rdquo;.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">I Macan ngon masi ia nepukin Ni M&eacute;saba ngajak pianakn&eacute; Ni Wingsali. I Macan ngomong k&eacute;n&eacute;, &rdquo;Ih, Iba buron, nyen jatin&eacute; Iba bani mai ka alas&eacute;? Kai an&eacute; kuasa di alas&eacute; en&eacute;&rdquo;! Masaut Ni M&eacute;saba, &rdquo;Ih, Iba macan. Iba mirib tusing nawang, uli awak kain&eacute; bisa pesu api. Di tanduk kain&eacute; Ida Sang Hyang Siwa an&eacute; malinggih. Kai kaliwat sakti, tusing buungan Iba bakal amah kai. K&eacute;to gretakn&eacute; Ni M&eacute;saba saha ng&eacute;ngkotang tandukn&eacute; tur mekecos. Jeg patipurug I Macan malaib. Matemu ia ngajak I Bojog, tur matakon k&eacute;n&eacute;. &ldquo;Wih&hellip; Beli Macan, anak ngudaiang Beli malaib?&rdquo;. I Macan masaut, &rdquo;Beli jejeh nepukin buron tawah. Awakn&eacute; pol&eacute;ng tandukn&eacute; lanying&rdquo;. Kacawis ban I Lutung, &rdquo;Ento sing ja l&eacute;nan tek&eacute;n I Kambing. Tiang mamusuh bebuyutan ngajak ia. Jalan jani malipetan bareng-bareng alih!&rdquo;.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Masaut I Macan, &ldquo;B&eacute;h, y&eacute;n beli kema tusing buungan beli mati, waluya ngejotang bangk&eacute;. Cai gancang men&eacute;k kayu, kal &eacute;lah ban makecos&rdquo;. I Bojog buin ngomong, &rdquo;Y&eacute;n beli sangsaya, jalan tegul bangkiang&eacute;, kant&eacute;tang ikuh&eacute;!&rdquo;. Guguna munyin I Bojog&eacute; tek&eacute;n I Macan. Ditu pada nyambung ikuh, tur pada negul bangkiang. Kacrita n&eacute; jani, suba neked di arepan Ni M&eacute;saban&eacute;. Ni M&eacute;saba masebeng &eacute;gar tur mamunyi, &rdquo;Uh, Cai Bojog teka. Dugas Cain&eacute; kalah matoh-tohan, majanji lakar nyerahang macan patpat. An&eacute; jani mara aukud Cai teka ngaba Macan. Nah, yadin k&eacute;to kanggoang embok masi, sedeng melaha embok ngidamang b&eacute; macan.&rdquo; Mara k&eacute;to munyin&eacute; Ni M&eacute;saba, I Macan kaliwat jejehn&eacute;, tur ngrengkeng k&eacute;n&eacute;. &rdquo;B&eacute;h, id&eacute;w&eacute;k bayahanga utang n&eacute; t&eacute;k&eacute;n I Bojog, &rdquo; Ban kaliwat jejehn&eacute;, ditu lantas ia malaib patipurug. I Bojog brag&eacute;d&eacute;ga. Pamuput ajaka dadua ulung di jurang&eacute; maimbuh tep&eacute;n batu bulitan ged&eacute; pesan. Kacerita, mati I Macan tek&eacute;n I Bojog. Nah, k&eacute;to tuah gegaman&eacute;, amun apa ja wan&eacute;n&eacute; wiadin kereng&eacute;, y&eacute;ning madasar belog tusing bisa ng&eacute;kadaya, sinah lakar nepukin sengkala buka I Macan.</span></p>', 'kambingmacan.png', NULL),
(13, 'PAN BALANG TAMAK', '<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Kacerita ada karma banjar an&eacute; sugih nanging dayan&eacute; pait, mapungkusan Pan Balang Tamak. Pan Balang Tamak, ia sugih pesan tur dueg makanda, tusing ta&eacute;n nyak kalah. Ento kranan&eacute; liunan karma d&eacute;san&eacute; tusing ieng tek&eacute;n Pan Balang Tamak. Y&eacute;n tuah dadi k&eacute;, apanga ia mati wiadin makisid uli d&eacute;san&eacute; totonan. Sedek dina anu, paum d&eacute;san&eacute; bakal nayanang Pan Balang Tamak, apanga ia kena danda. Panyarikan d&eacute;san&eacute; nund&eacute;n ngarahin Pan Balang Tamak, k&eacute;n&eacute; arah-arahn&eacute;, &rdquo;Ih Pan Balang Tamak, buin mani semengan mara tuun siap, d&eacute;san&eacute; luas ka gunung ngalih kayu, bakal anggon menahin bal&eacute; agung. Ny&eacute;n ja kas&eacute;pan ngayah, bakal kena danda.&rdquo; K&eacute;to arah-arah&eacute; tek&eacute;n Pan Balang Tamak. Buin manin&eacute; semangan mara tuun siap, saja krama d&eacute;san&eacute; makejang suba ngayah, Pan Balang Tamak enu jumahn&eacute; ngantosang siapn&eacute; an&eacute; makaem tuun uli bengbengan&eacute;. Makelo ia ngantiang, tond&eacute;n masih siapn&eacute; tuun. Suba tengai, mara siapn&eacute; tuun, ditu mara ia majalan, nututin d&eacute;san&eacute; luas ngalih kayu ka alas&eacute;. Tepukina krama d&eacute;san&eacute; suba pada mulih negen kayu, Pan Balang Tamak milu malipetan.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;Kacrita suba neked jumah, lantas d&eacute;san&eacute; paum, maumang Pan Balang Tamak lakar kena danda, krana ia tuara nuutang araharah&eacute;. Ditu laut d&eacute;san&eacute; nund&eacute;n ngarahin Pan Balang Tamak. Kacrita jani, Pan Balang Tamak suba teka, lantas klian d&eacute;san&eacute; mabaos, &rdquo;Ih Pan Balang Tamak, jani Cai patut mayah danda&rdquo;. Masaut panyarikan d&eacute;san&eacute;, &rdquo;Sawir&eacute;h Cai tuara ngidepang arah-arah&eacute; ngalih kayu ka gunung.&rdquo; &rdquo;Mangkin dumun jero, sampunang nganikang tiang tuara ngidepang arah-arah&eacute;! D&eacute;ning arah-arah&eacute; kraman&eacute; patut ngayah semengan mara tuun siap&eacute;, tiang sampun ngayah duk ayam tiang&eacute; tuun uli makaem di bengbengan&eacute;.&rdquo; K&eacute;to munyin Pan Balang Tamak&eacute;, dadi d&eacute;san&eacute; sing ada ngelah keneh nglawan.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Kacrita buin maninn&eacute; Pan Balang Tamak karaahin ngaba sengauk, bekel menahin bal&eacute; agung. Ngaba kon&eacute; ia sanggah wug ka pura d&eacute;sa tur ngraos k&eacute;n&eacute;, &rdquo;En&eacute; sanggah wug, apanga benahanga baan d&eacute;san&eacute;.&rdquo; Dadi ngon krama d&eacute;san&eacute; tek&eacute;n abet Pan Balang Tamak&eacute;, awanan liu krama d&eacute;san&eacute; dot nga&eacute;nang ia apang pelih. Buin maninn&eacute;, Pan Balang Tamak kaarahin maboros ka gunung. K&eacute;n&eacute; arah-arah&eacute;, &rdquo;Elingang benjang kraman&eacute; maboros, mangda muat cicing galak. Sira ja ten madu&eacute; cicing galak, jagi keni danda.&rdquo; Krama d&eacute;san&eacute; suba pada yatna, an&eacute; tuara ngelah cicing galak, suba pada nyilih. Pan Balang Tamak ngelah kuluk bengil aukud buin tuara pati nyidang malaib.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Kacerita buin maninn&eacute; las d&eacute;san&eacute; maboros, tur pada ngaba cicing galak-galak, ngliwat pangkung lan gr&eacute;mb&eacute;ngan dalem-dalem. Pan Balang Tamak majalan paling durina sambilanga nyangkol cicingn&eacute;. Mara ia neked sig gr&eacute;mb&eacute;ng&eacute;, sing dadi baana ngliwat, lantas ia nga&eacute; daya apang kraman&eacute; teka nyagjagin, laut jerit-jerit. &rdquo;Bangkung tra gigina, bangkung tra gigina.&rdquo; Mara dingeha baan kraman&eacute;, kad&eacute;na timpaln&eacute; nepukin bangkung, lantas pada nyagjagin. Mara neked ditu tepukina Pan Balang Tamak jerit-jerit, lantas takonina: &rdquo;Apa kendehang Pan Balang Tamak?&rdquo; Masaut Pan Balang Tamak, k&eacute;n&eacute;, &rdquo;Pangkung tara ada titina.&rdquo; B&eacute;h, sengap kraman&eacute;, belog-beloga. Payu baangina titi, gantin Pan Balang Tamak&eacute; tuara kena danda.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Suba neked di alas&eacute;, lantas krama d&eacute;san&eacute; pada ngandupang cicingn&eacute; ka tengah ebet&eacute;, ada ngepung kidang, ada ngepung c&eacute;l&eacute;ng, ada ngepung manjangan, ada ngongkong bojog di punyan kayun&eacute;. Pan Balang Tamak kelad-kelid sambilanga nyangkol cicingn&eacute; mara neked di punyan k&eacute;tk&eacute;t&eacute;. Jani, entunganga cicingn&eacute; ka punyan k&eacute;tk&eacute;t&eacute;. Kaing-kaing cicingn&eacute; ngengsut, tusing bisa tuun, tusing bisa men&eacute;k. K&eacute;n&eacute; Pan Balang Tamak ngraos, &rdquo;Ih jero krama d&eacute;sa sami, tingalin ja cicing tiang&eacute; ngragas ka punyan k&eacute;tk&eacute;t&eacute;. Sira madu&eacute; cicing galak buka cicing tiang&eacute;? Mangkin tiang ngen&eacute;ng danda krama d&eacute;san&eacute;, wir&eacute;h ten w&eacute;nten madu&eacute; cicing galak buka cicing tiang&eacute;.&rdquo; Krama d&eacute;san&eacute; tusing ada bisa masaut, payu kenaina danda baan Pan Balang Tamak. Suba kon&eacute; k&eacute;to lantas pada mulih suud maboros.&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Kacerita maninn&eacute; buin kaarahin Pan Balang Tamak, d&eacute;san&eacute; lakar sangkep di bal&eacute; banjar&eacute;. Mara Pan Balang Tamak ningeh araharah&eacute; k&eacute;to, ia nga&eacute; jaja uli injin, bakal anggona melog-melog krama d&eacute;san&eacute;. Majalan ngayah sangkep, Pan Balang Tamak ngaba jaja injin, mapulung-pulung amun tain cicing&eacute;, laut pejangnga di sendin bal&eacute; banjar&eacute; tur kecirina y&eacute;h. Nyak cara tain cicing. Kacrita suba pada carem krama d&eacute;san&eacute;, lantas Pan Balang Tamak mauar-uar k&eacute;n&eacute;, &rdquo;Ih Jero makejang, ny&eacute;n ja bani ngajeng tain cicing&eacute; totonan, tiang sanggup ngupahin pipis.&rdquo; Masaut panyarikan&eacute;, &rdquo;Bes sigug abet&eacute; mapeta, ny&eacute;n men nyak naar tain cicing? Tegarang Cai ngamah! Lamun bani, icang ja ngupahin pipis.&rdquo; Mara k&eacute;to, jeg &eacute;nggal Pan Balang Tamak naar kanti telah. Dadi bengong krama d&eacute;san&eacute; nyingakin Pan Balang Tamak bani naar tain cicing. To makrana, krama d&eacute;san&eacute; dendaina ban Pan Balang Tamak. Dadi ngancan nyangetang brangtin gedeg kraman&eacute;, dot lakar ng&eacute;kadaya, apang sida ja ngalahang Pan Balang Tamak.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Bin manin&eacute; buin Pan Balang Tamak kaarahin, tusing dadi ngenjek karang anak muah maalih-alihan ka abian anak. Yen bani mamurug, bakal kena danda. K&eacute;to arah-arahan&eacute;. Yadin k&eacute;to, Pan Balang Tamak tuara k&eacute;weh. Ditu ia ng&eacute;kadaya, g&eacute;r&eacute;ta pulet&eacute; an&eacute; di sisin peken&eacute; anggona abian pagehina lidi, tur apesina ban benang. Suba jani ram&eacute; peken&eacute;, ada anak makita masakit basang, lantas nylibsib ka pulet&eacute;, laut masuak Pan Balang Tamak, &rdquo;Ih jero d&eacute;sa, tiang nandanin anak ngamaling ka abian tiang&eacute;.&rdquo; Dadi cengang anak&eacute; n&eacute; masakit basang &eacute;ndahanga ban Pan Balang Tamak. Masaut anak&eacute; masakit basang, &rdquo;Apa salah tiang&eacute;, muah dadi nagih danda jeron&eacute;?&rdquo; Masaut Pan Balang Tamak, &rdquo;Jeron&eacute; macelep ka abian tiang&eacute; tur mamaling pamula-mulaan tiang&eacute;. Ento apa bongkos jeron&eacute;?&rdquo; Mara ungkabanga, saja mrareket pulet&eacute; di kamenn&eacute;. Puputn&eacute; payu ia dendana baan Pan Balang Tamak.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">K&eacute;weh pesan krama desane ngencanin Pan Balang Tamak, daya kudang daya singa ada mintulin. N&eacute; jani k&eacute;neh d&eacute;san&eacute; bakal nunasang paporongan tek&eacute;n anak&eacute; agung. Gelisang cerita, cuba kon&eacute; kic&eacute;n cetik an&eacute; paling sagerda, apanga Pan Balang Tamak mati. Kocap Pan Balang Tamak suba ningeh ortan&eacute; ento, ngomong ia tek&eacute;n kurenan&eacute;. &rdquo;Yen awak&eacute; suba mati, gantungin bok awak&eacute; temblilingan. Suba k&eacute;to sed&eacute;d&eacute;ngang di piasan&eacute;. Pagelah-gelahan&eacute; pesuang, jang di bal&eacute; sakanem&eacute;, rurubin ban kamen putih sambilang pangelingin. Nah, bangk&eacute;n awak&eacute; wadahin peti, pejang jumah met&eacute;n.&rdquo;&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Gelisang crita, suba Pan Balang Tamak mati ngamah cetik paican anak&eacute; agung. Lantas M&eacute;n Balang Tamak nuutang buka pabesen Pan Balang Tamak&eacute;. Kacrita d&eacute;san&eacute; ngintip Pan Balang Tamak, mati kalawan tan matin&eacute;. Mara neked jumah Pan Balang Tamak&eacute;, Pan Balang Tamak nyed&eacute;d&eacute;g di piasan&eacute; sambilanga mamantra ngambahang bok. Ditu d&eacute;san&eacute; maselselan, pada ngorahang cetik&eacute; jel&eacute;k. Lantas d&eacute;san&eacute; buin parek ka puri, ngaturang panguninga yen Pan Balang Tamak tuara mati. Mara k&eacute;to bendu anak&eacute; agung, d&eacute;ning cetik&eacute; kaaturang tuara saged. Lantas ida ngandika, &rdquo;K&eacute;nk&eacute;n cetik&eacute; dadi tuara ngamatiang, indayang awak&eacute; ngasanin. Mara ajengang ida abedik, prajani ida s&eacute;da.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">M&eacute;n Balang Tamak ningeh orta, yen anak&eacute; agung suba s&eacute;da ngajengang cetik, .lantas ia ng&eacute;kanang bangk&eacute;n kurenann&eacute; buka an&eacute; suba. Kacrita suba sanja, ada dusta ajaka patpat mapiguman, bakal mamaling ka umah Pan Balang Tamak&eacute;. Mara enota kurenan Pan Balang Tamak&eacute; mangelingin kurenann&eacute; di bal&eacute; sakanem&eacute;, lantas ia macelep ka umah met&eacute;n, tepukina peti ged&eacute; buin baat pesan, laut sanglonga, senamina, tegena ajaka patpat. Suba kon&eacute; neked ka tengah bet&eacute;, ngraos timpaln&eacute;, &rdquo;Dini suba gagah!&rdquo; Masaut timpaln&eacute;, &rdquo;Maebo bangk&eacute; dini, jalan indayang dituan.&rdquo; Lantas kisidanga masih maebo bangk&eacute;. Buin ngaros timpaln&eacute;, &rdquo;Jalan suba aba ka pura d&eacute;sa, ditu ny&eacute;n bani ngutang bangkaan.&rdquo; Masaut timpaln&eacute;, &rdquo;Jalan!&rdquo; Lantas tegena petin&eacute;, abana ka pura. Mara neked ditu, lantas ungkabanga. Mara enota bangk&eacute;n Pan Balang Tamak&eacute; nyengkang, lantas plaibina, kutanga petin&eacute; ditu.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Kacrita maninn&eacute; mara galang kangin, nuju jero mangku ngaturang canang ka pura‟ mara nengok di kori agung&eacute;, tingalina ada peti ged&eacute; di natah piasan&eacute;, lantas jero mangku masila tiding sambilanga nyumbah: &rdquo;Betaran titiang&eacute; mapaica, bataran titiang&eacute; mapaica.&rdquo; Baan sing ada bani mungkah, ngantiang apanga pepek krama d&eacute;san&eacute; teka. Mara teka ukud nyumbah, teka ukud nyumbah. Suba kon&eacute; pepek pada nyumbah, lantas petin&eacute; bungkaha, nget bangk&eacute;n Pan Balang Tamak&eacute; nyengku, dadi tengkejut kraman&eacute;, buin pada misuhin bangk&eacute;n Pan Balang Tamak&eacute;. Ento japin pisuhin, mlutang ya, kadung suba bakat sumbah. Puput d&eacute;san&eacute; tuyuh m&eacute;anin muah nanem bangk&eacute;n Pan Balang Tamak&eacute;. K&eacute;to katuturannya.</span></p>', 'balang2.png', NULL);
